<item>
            <title>[AMQ-3289] ActiveMQ has problems storing &gt;4K messages in Oracle</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-3289</link>
                <project id="12311210" key="AMQ">ActiveMQ Classic</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The oracle persistence adapter extends the blob jdbc adapter but it has gotten out of sync with the method overrides. @Override to the rescue for the future.&lt;br/&gt;
The blob adapter uses native blob streaming to insert data (which can accommodate &amp;gt; 4k) but it has been out of step for some time.&lt;br/&gt;
The implementations need to be brought into line w.r.t to the api, schema and locking.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
