&lt;p&gt;Need someone with a handy Oracle install to validate the fix. Verify send received persistent messages &amp;gt; 4k&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Kicked off a snapshot that will be done in an hour or so.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13022089" author="gtully" created="Wed, 20 Apr 2011 12:13:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It looks like the ojdbc6 drivers avoid this problem as they use the default adapter.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
